# Testing

- Test scripts load env vars from `.env.local` directly via `dotenv.config({ path: ".env.local" })`. Never rely on `DOTENV_CONFIG_PATH` or `dotenv/config` bare import.
- Run provider tests with `npm run test:providers`. Run all tests with `npm run test`.
- Test audio files live in `test-audio/`.
